<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Secure E-Voting System</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #e3f2fd, #bbdefb);
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        nav {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #00796b, #004d40);
            padding: 16px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            transition: color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.15);
            color: #c8e6c9;
        }
        .key-features li {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #8ff6ea, #004d40);
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .key-features li:hover {
            transform: scale(1.07);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .register-btn {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #00796b, #004d40);
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .register-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #004d40, #00796b);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .register-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 font-sans">
    <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-700 to-green-500 text-white py-8 text-center text-5xl font-bold shadow-lg">
        Secure E-Voting System
    </header>
    
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-center space-x-8 text-xl">
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/votedetails">User  Details</a>
            <a href="/auth">Authentication Process</a>
            <a href="/decrypto">Voter Registration</a>
            <a href="/vote">Vote Casting</a>
            <a href="/">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    <section class="container mx-auto p-12" id="about">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center" id="greeting"></h2> <!-- Greeting message -->
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" id="user">
            hello Our secure e-voting system ensures transparency and reliability in elections. By leveraging QR-code authentication and visual cryptography, we provide a safe and scalable voting solution.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-8">Key Features:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-8 mt-4 space-y-4 key-features">
            <li><strong>QR-Code Authentication:</strong> Secure and intuitive voter authentication using QR-codes.</li>
            <li><strong>Visual Cryptography:</strong> Ensures secure decryption while maintaining voter privacy.</li>
            <li><strong>Real-Time Vote Counting:</strong> Automates the tallying process for quick and accurate results.</li>
            <li><strong>Multi-Device Support:</strong> Compatible with smartphones, tablets, and desktop systems.</li>
            <li><strong>Scalability:</strong> Designed to handle elections with large voter turnout efficiently.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
            <a href="auth" class="btn btn-outline-success">Register Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-700 to-green-500 text-white text-center py-8 mt-8 text-xl shadow-md">
        &copy; 2025 Secure E-Voting System | Ensuring Safe and Transparent Elections
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // function openLoginModal() {
        //     var loginModal = new bootstrap.Modal(document.getElementById('loginModal'));
        //     loginModal.show();
        // }
        
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const loggedInUser  = localStorage.getItem('name');
            if (loggedInUser ) {
                document.getElementById('greeting').innerText = `Hey! ${loggedInUser }`;
            } else {
                document.getElementById('greeting').innerText = 'Welcome to the Secure E-Voting System';
            }

        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>